SELECT id, 'Financial Risk Management Framework', 'Develop comprehensive financial risk management framework for [COMPANY_NAME] covering all material financial risks. Assess foreign exchange risk from international operations and develop hedging strategy using forwards, options, or natural hedges. Analyse interest rate risk on debt portfolio and evaluate fixing versus floating decisions. Review commodity price exposure and hedging mechanisms. Evaluate credit risk from customer concentration and establish credit insurance or limits. Assess liquidity risk and maintain adequate facility headroom. Review insurance coverages for material risks. Establish risk appetite statements, monitoring metrics, and governance framework. Include compliance with AASB requirements for hedge accounting and derivative disclosures.', 10
FROM prompt_packs WHERE name = 'CFO Financial Leadership';